name: #3. INES "THE BUILDER" AMOROSO
description:
When plans need a-makin', "The Builder" gets a-shakin'

The design is inspired by artist Piet Mondrian and the De Stijl art movement. The Mondrian aesthetic is significant to the artist as it was featured in the first NFT he ever purchased. It was also featured in his first art piece on hic et nunc which utilized the 'Swatch OBJKTs' system.

"A cat without a grin, but a grin without a cat."
"What has 13 hearts, but no other organs?"
"What is broken when spoken?"

'r' toggles auto-rotate. 'l' toggles cursor following.

Artist: Yazid
